  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was not unusual to have 20, 30 people, little cousins and the laughter and guffawing, the-- you know, the fooling around and the chasing each other.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, it was just a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it doesn't sound like a great thing here, but it was a great thing there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- we just-- I just miss it terribly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I look back, it was just a wonderful, wonderful experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Is there anything you'd like to add about before the war before we change tapes in a moment?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would just like to say that, regardless where I've been and what I've seen and what had happened to me, I have to say that my roots are on that street, in that place, in that city because that was a wonderful-- that was a wonderful memory to me.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if, as a child, you can relate to one specific, one wonderful thing, that is the time and that is the place that it happened to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what I miss most, and perhaps wouldn't have traded for anything else if I knew better, if life didn't play another choice for me.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
